Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I looked all day for a place to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But no vacancy signs went on for miles~
