Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't ask when you're as desp'rate as I~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You don't ask why~ when it's Lyra and Bon-Bon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I watched them together while under the weather and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Couldn't believe my eyes
