Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They'll share the rest of their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It made me blue and a little bit green
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That they were flushed red with love
